\b Tone
\b0 \
\
Tone is a Golem--a clay doll with a soul attached to it. She is tacit and curious, though her infant-like mind causes her problems when it comes to learning something new. Given that she has Devyn's soul attachment, Tone feels an incomprehensible bond with her maker similar to that of a mother and child.\
\
====\
